  },
  {
    icon: 'badge',
    title: 'Loyalty, CRM, SCRM',
    cn: '会员与营销',
    body: 'SCRM platforms for member tagging (会员标签), behavioural tracking, automated journeys, personalised messaging through corporate WeChat. Global Salesforce, HubSpot, Zendesk setups wire in through connectors.',
